<template><div class="page"><div class="page-head"><div><h2>系统运行与审计日志</h2><p>记录主体登录和关键业务操作，为系统后台管理提供审计依据。</p></div><el-radio-group v-model="kind" @change="load"><el-radio-button label="operation">操作日志</el-radio-button><el-radio-button label="login">登录日志</el-radio-button></el-radio-group></div><div class="system-bar"><span><i class="el-icon-success" /> 后端服务：运行正常</span><span><i class="el-icon-success" /> MySQL数据库：连接正常</span><span><i class="el-icon-success" /> 区块链存证服务：运行正常</span></div><el-table :data="list" border><el-table-column prop="username" label="操作账号" /><el-table-column prop="role" label="角色" /><el-table-column prop="action" label="操作类型" /><el-table-column prop="detail" label="详细信息" /><el-table-column prop="created_at" label="记录时间" width="190" /></el-table></div></template>
